## ✅ Final Remarks

The OptiCrop system demonstrates how artificial intelligence and machine learning can be effectively applied in agriculture. By transforming soil and environmental data into meaningful crop recommendations, the system helps farmers make informed decisions, increase agricultural productivity, and contribute to sustainable farming practices.

### 🌾 Smart Farming Today for a Better Tomorrow 🌍
